<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>OTP Verification - Zypsii</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #b9138c; /* Zypsii primary color */
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .header img {
            width: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .otp-box {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            color: #333;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dqoknzboz/image/upload/v1745737433/0dae3459-63d4-407e-8151-68a17e137ec6_qvs5fy.jpg" alt="Zypsii Logo"> <!-- Replace with your actual logo -->
        <h2>Zypsii</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h1>Your OTP Code</h1>
        <p>Use the following OTP to reset your password. This OTP is valid for 10 minutes only.</p>

        <div class="otp-box">
            <%= otp %>
        </div>

        <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Zypsii. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
